Package nl.captcha.servlet

Class Summary
CaptchaServletUtil  
ChineseCaptchaServlet Generate a CAPTCHA image/answer pair using Chinese characters.
SimpleCaptchaServlet Generates, displays, and stores in session a 200x50 CAPTCHA image with sheared black text, a solid dark grey background, and a straight, slanted red line through the text.
StickyCaptchaServlet Builds a 200x50 (default) CAPTCHA and attaches it to the session.
